                            <comment id="12849210" author="jramos" created="Wed, 24 Mar 2010 14:59:28 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I checked in a fix and tested directly with UriBuilder.  Let me know if this fixes your LinkBuilders scenario.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12849227" author="hudson" created="Wed, 24 Mar 2010 15:37:07 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Integrated in Wink-Trunk-JDK1.5 #297 (See &lt;a href=&quot;http://hudson.zones.apache.org/hudson/job/Wink-Trunk-JDK1.5/297/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://hudson.zones.apache.org/hudson/job/Wink-Trunk-JDK1.5/297/&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;br/&gt;
    []: Don&apos;t include path templates in scheme portion of path&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12851913" author="shayts7" created="Wed, 31 Mar 2010 15:38:43 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;It fixed my problem, Thanks!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
